Another notable trend in the market is the focus on security and data protection in semiconductor IP solutions. With the proliferation of IoT devices and connectivity platforms, there is a heightened emphasis on integrating robust security features into semiconductor designs to safeguard sensitive data and prevent cyber threats. Market players are actively developing encryption technologies, secure boot mechanisms, and hardware-based security solutions to address security concerns in connected devices and networks.

